text: Yallih niqmatay sin amol yani kassita, Qaad deqsita marih lakal Baaxo ciggila mara sin abeemil, cijri deqsitta baaxól dabqah sin hee tet cuguubal kaxxa Qarwa xissittaanaah Qaleela Qarwah uruttan waqdi, toysa Yallih niqmootay sin amol tani kassitaay baaxó uma taamoomit mabaysina baaxó uma taamat baysa mara akkuk
